Actually, your problem is caused by OrbitControls.
`setPointerCapture` in OrbitControls disable mouse click. see https://github.com/mrdoob/three.js/issues/22353

## Solution

1. don't attach OrbitControls to `CSS2DRenderer#domElement`, use `WebGLRenderer#domElement` instead.
2. make mouse events transparent on `CSS2DRenderer#domElement`.
3. revert mouse events on each element.

https://jsfiddle.net/2mL48djq/

```diff
- const controls = new OrbitControls( camera, labelRenderer.domElement );
+ const controls = new OrbitControls( camera, renderer.domElement );

+ labelRenderer.domElement.style.pointerEvents = 'none';
+ earthDiv.style.pointerEvents = 'auto';
+ moonDiv.style.pointerEvents = 'auto';
```

