`gl_FrontFacing` depends on the winding order. When `side = THREE.BackSide`, the winding order is reversed for WebGLRenderer.

Use this pattern, instead
```glsl
void main() {
    #ifdef FLIP_SIDED
        gl_FragColor = vec4( 0, 0, 1, 1 );
    #elif defined( DOUBLE_SIDED )
        gl_FragColor = ( gl_FrontFacing ) ? vec4( 1, 0, 0, 1 ) : vec4( 0, 0, 1, 1 );
    #else
        gl_FragColor = vec4( 1, 0, 0, 1 );
    #endif
}
```

